---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy — Global Wealth Portfolio" description="How we handle your data, security measures, and your rights under DPDPA, GDPR, and CCPA.">
  <section class="container-page page-section pt-3xl pb-2xl max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-caption-mono text-gold mb-xs">Privacy &amp; Security</p>
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-lg">Your data stays yours.</h1>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio is designed with <strong>privacy by design</strong> and
      <strong>security by default</strong>. This policy describes how we protect your
      data and your rights under <strong>DPDPA (India)</strong>,
      <strong>GDPR (EU/UK)</strong>, and <strong>CCPA (California)</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">1. Data controller &amp; contact</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Global Wealth Portfolio operates as a data controller. For any privacy-related
      requests or concerns:
    </p>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Use the contact form on our website. Response time: within 30 days (DPDPA &amp; GDPR compliant).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">2. Data collection &amp; purpose</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      We collect the minimum data necessary for the service to function:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-lg space-y-xs text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <li><strong>Financial data</strong> (investments, expenses, goals, EMI) — stored in your browser's <code>localStorage</code> for offline use. Never sent to our servers.</li>
      <li><strong>Blog subscribers</strong> — email address only, stored in encrypted Cloudflare KV, used solely to send new-post notifications. Consent obtained at time of subscription. Unsubscribe one-click at any time.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage analytics</strong> — anonymized page view data via Google Analytics (G-J020W8NDX9). No personally identifiable information is collected. You may opt out via browser privacy settings.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising</strong> — contextual ads via Google AdSense. No targeted advertising based on your financial data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">3. Security measures</h2>
    <div class="space-y-md text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <div class="card-soft p-md">
        <p class="text-body-sm-strong text-ink mb-xs">🔒 HTTPS with TLS 1.3</p>
        <p>All data in transit is encrypted using TLS 1.3 via Cloudflare's edge network. HSTS is enforced (<code>max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload</code>).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-md">
        <p class="text-body-sm-strong text-ink mb-xs">🔐 AES-256-GCM encryption at rest</p>
        <p>You can optionally encrypt all localStorage data with AES-256-GCM using a passphrase (Settings → Encryption). Key derivation uses PBKDF2 with 600,000 iterations. The passphrase is never stored — data remains encrypted at rest until you unlock it in a session.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-md">
        <p class="text-body-sm-strong text-ink mb-xs">🛡️ Access controls &amp; audit logs</p>
        <p>All data changes are recorded in an append-only audit log with timestamps and action descriptions. The admin panel is protected by a passphrase with optional OTP-based password reset via EmailJS.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-md">
        <p class="text-body-sm-strong text-ink mb-xs">📦 Encrypted server storage</p>
        <p>Server-side data (blog posts, subscriber emails) is stored in Cloudflare KV, which encrypts all data at rest using AES-256. Admin API endpoints require a Bearer token (<code>ADMIN_TOKEN</code>).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-md">
        <p class="text-body-sm-strong text-ink mb-xs">🧹 Local processing</p>
        <p>Bank statement OCR (Tesseract.js) and PDF import run entirely in your browser. Uploaded files are never transmitted to any server and are discarded after processing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">4. Your rights (DPDPA / GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-body-md text-body border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <th class="text-left py-sm pr-md font-medium text-ink">Right</th>
            <th class="text-left py-sm font-medium text-ink">How to exercise</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Access / data portability</td>
            <td class="py-sm">Settings → Import/Export → Export JSON</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Rectification</td>
            <td class="py-sm">Edit data directly in the app (all changes are local)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Deletion (right to be forgotten)</td>
            <td class="py-sm">Settings → Reset all data (local). Unsubscribe link in every email (server).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Withdraw consent</td>
            <td class="py-sm">Click unsubscribe in any newsletter email, or delete your data via Settings</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-hairline">
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Opt out of sale (CCPA)</td>
            <td class="py-sm">We do not sell your personal information. No action needed.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-sm pr-md">Lodge a complaint</td>
            <td class="py-sm">Contact us via the website contact form</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">5. Consent &amp; lawful basis</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      We process data on the following lawful bases under GDPR:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-lg space-y-xs text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <li><strong>Consent</strong> — newsletter subscriptions (explicit opt-in, verifiable, withdrawable)</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — anonymized analytics to improve the service</li>
      <li><strong>Performance of a contract</strong> — core app functionality (financial tracking)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Under DPDPA, consent is obtained through explicit action (typing your email and clicking Subscribe). Consent logs are maintained in the audit trail.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">6. Data retention</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Local data persists until you clear your browser data or use "Reset all data".
      Subscriber emails are retained until the subscriber unsubscribes (DELETE request)
      or requests removal. Analytics data is retained per Google's data retention policy (26 months).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">7. Third-party services</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-lg space-y-xs text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> (CDN, DNS, KV storage, edge network) — <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> (anonymized page views) — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> (contextual ads) — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> (typography) — <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
      <li><strong>Resend</strong> (newsletter email delivery) — <a href="https://resend.com/privacy" class="text-link hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">8. International transfers</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      Data may be processed on Cloudflare's global edge network (GDPR-compliant Standard Contractual Clauses in place).
      Local data stays on your device and never crosses your browser's origin.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">9. Policy updates</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-md">
      This policy was last updated on June 15, 2026. Changes will be posted here.
      For significant changes, returning users will see a notice on the dashboard.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Contact &amp; DPO</h2>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body">
      Data Protection Officer: Sourabhsingh Rajput<br />
      Use the contact form on the website.<br />
      Response within 30 days as required by DPDPA &amp; GDPR.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
